  fhir:description [ fhir:v "Local codes defined by the OGCA IG for concepts that do not yet have\nan established representation in LOINC, SNOMED CT, or mCODE. These codes are migration\ncandidates and should be retired in favor of standard codes as they become available."] ; # 
