  fhir:purpose [ fhir:v "mCODE Migration Candidate — individual codes submitted to LOINC and SNOMED CT.\nThis code system will be retired once standard codes are assigned. It is NOT intended to\nbe a permanent artifact of this IG. See the mCODE Candidates page for the migration plan."] ; # 
